data.description: Welcome to a charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in Lithonia, GA. This residence features a main-floor bedroom with an attached full bath, ideal for guests or an office. Enjoy the convenience of 2 staircases, vaulted ceilings, and a bonus room. The formal living and dining rooms are perfect for gatherings. With a 2-car garage, spacious driveway, and vaulted ceilings, this home offers comfort and style. Don't miss this opportunity to own a versatile and well-located property in Lithonia.
